{"tid":2507781,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（投胎）廣西狂男闖幼園斬師生 多名幼童浴血躺地","createTime":"2021-04-28T08:50:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T08:52:01.000Z","uid":58416,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e6e94ff8952c5d421a230b9299327726a515448f","tid":2507781,"uid":58416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T08:50:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeZHA8skG6aCSsSqKakwNSkHzrfKJYQd6degDpssd4LDC?filename=U8P7VS3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU8P7VS3.png&h=1f4cfcc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n國家主席習近平正在廣西考察，當地隨即傳出嚴重傷人案；一名25歲男子於周三（28日）下午約2時突然闖入廣西北流市新豐鎮健樂幼兒園，並持刀襲擊老師和學生，導致多人受傷，多名幼童浴血躺在地上。該男子現時已被警方拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n內媒引述現場一名目擊者指，當日他路過北流市新豐鎮健樂幼兒園時，看到一名男子正被3名警員從幼兒園內押送出來，「還有小孩子頭部流着血從幼兒園裏出來。」附近一名商舖老闆亦表示，男疑犯年紀不大，其行為舉止似乎有些異常；後來有路人看到該男子持刀斬人後，便拿着木棍衝進幼兒園內將其圍住，警方隨後到場將其制伏。<br />\n<br />\n傷者現時正在新豐鎮衛生院接受治療。警方表示，男疑犯的年齡約25歲，現時已被拘捕，並強調他「可能精神有問題」；至於事件中有多名老師和學生受傷，部分受傷較嚴重的正在接受搶救。"},{"pid":"d44b6e64d27b86376b719ed718b728da13c06b83","tid":2507781,"uid":83328,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T08:50:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/520936/org/d5f8f9e726beb1506da099d832179eb1.PNG/_uVrzSiJARDQtGFvZekG48je5fdZpP9HrxhKza8YSs0?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F520936%2Forg%2Fd5f8f9e726beb1506da099d832179eb1.PNG%2F_uVrzSiJARDQtGFvZekG48je5fdZpP9HrxhKza8YSs0%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=8299c489&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c90431022b202acc4737c7d1af06eb7647181085","tid":2507781,"uid":58416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d44b6e64d27b86376b719ed718b728da13c06b83","tid":2507781,"uid":83328,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T08:50:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/520936/org/d5f8f9e726beb1506da099d832179eb1.PNG/_uVrzSiJARDQtGFvZekG48je5fdZpP9HrxhKza8YSs0?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thu